<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="T" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Tree" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Tree,</orth> a plant with a woody and perennial stem: <bibl n="shak. ven 152" default="NO" valid="yes">Ven. 152</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ven 152" default="NO" valid="yes">Ven. 152</bibl> <bibl n="shak. ven 152" default="NO" valid="yes">Ven. 152</bibl> <bibl n="shak. son 12.5" default="NO" valid="yes">Sonn. 12, 5</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. pp 135" default="NO" valid="yes">Pilgr. 135</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. pp 135" default="NO" valid="yes">Pilgr. 135</bibl> <bibl n="shak. pht 2" default="NO" valid="yes">Phoen. 2</bibl> <cit><quote>(the sole Arabian t.).</quote> <bibl n="shak. tmp 2.2.128" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. II, 2, 128</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. tmp 3.2.40" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 2, 40</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tmp 3.3.23" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 3, 23</bibl> <cit><quote>(one t., the Phoenix' throne).</quote> <bibl n="shak. wiv 4.4.32" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. IV, 4, 32</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. wiv 5.5.83" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 5, 83</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lll 4.3.341" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL IV, 3, 341</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lll 5.2.285" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 2, 285</bibl> <cit><quote>(Dumain is mine, as sure as bark on t.).</quote> <bibl n="shak. lll 5.2.285" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 2, 285</bibl></cit> <bibl n="shak. mv 5.2.80" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. V, 2, 80</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ayl 2.1.16" default="NO" valid="yes">As II, 1, 16</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ayl 2.3.63" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 3, 63</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ayl 3.2.9" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 2, 9</bibl>. 249 (<emph>Jove's t.,</emph> i. e. the oak). <bibl n="shak. r2 2.3.53" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 II, 3, 53</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 2.4.471" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A II, 4, 471</bibl> <cit><quote>(the t. may be known by the fruit).</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h6 2.4.41" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A II, 4, 41</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 2.1.96" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B II, 1, 96</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 2.5.49" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C II, 5, 49</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 5.2.14" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 2, 14</bibl> <cit><quote>(Jove's spreading t.).</quote> <bibl n="shak. tit 2.3.2" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. II, 3, 2</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. tit 5.1.47" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 1, 47</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tit 5.1.47" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 1, 47</bibl> <bibl n="shak. oth 5.2.15" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. V, 2, 15</bibl>. 350 <cit><quote>(Arabian --s).</quote> <bibl n="shak. cym 3.3.60" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. III, 3, 60</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. cym 5.5.264" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 5, 264</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. per 1.1.114" default="NO" valid="yes">Per. I, 1, 114</bibl> etc. cf. <emph>Cypress, Elder, Medlar, Pomegranate, Willow</emph> etc.
